cs.CR, cs.SE, cs.CY, cs.PL, cs.DC

This paper discusses a security system for the Web that addresses issues related to data privacy and protection. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also presents a system that is designed to work with all websites, which suggests that it involves software engineering (cs.SE) and possibly programming languages (cs.PL). Additionally, the system may involve issues related to cyber security (cs.CY) and distributed computing (cs.DC).
